events.name: EV011エマ盗賊団包囲網1-5自動実行

parameters: Do you want to enter the boss area?
Clea (Let's prepare first before doing that)
Thief Nora: Captain, you're safe, right!?

Thief Nora: I'm so relieved... I was really worried... I'm
so glad... *sniff*...

Clea: Now, how do we make the members of the Emma Thief Gang
retreat?

Priestess Sophia: We also need a way to escape from the
pursuers of the Imperial Army.

Mage Relm: It would be great if we had a place to hide...
Hmm...

Thief Nora: Don't worry about the details! The captain is
alive and everyone else is alive too.

Thief Nora: The place where everyone is together is the Emma
Thief Gang!

Captain Clevo: That's right... You're that kind of person,
huh.

Captain Clevo: The place where we are is the Emma Thief
Gang. I've also made up my mind... Thank you.

Thief Nora: Hehe, let's hurry and leave this place! There
are a lot of Imperial Army soldiers heading towards here!

Thief Nora: Captain...? You drew your knife... Is something
wrong...?

Captain Clevo: The Emma Thief Gang was formed by returning
soldiers who had their land taken away by the nobles.

Captain Clevo: After returning from that hellish
battlefield, I dragged my comrades back into the quagmire of
war.

Captain Clevo: I just wanted to live peaceful days, like
growing wheat...

Thief Nora: Don't worry, Captain! If it's you, you can
definitely lead everyone to the right place.

Captain Clevo: More than half of the Emma Thief Gang died in
this incident where we let those people die...
Captain Clevo: For the sake of my ideals.

Captain Clevo: That's why I'm willing to throw away all my
beliefs, ideals, and pride... in order to protect the
remaining members.

Captain Clevo: I need to fight alongside you all here for
the sake of the Emma Thief Gang.
Thief Nora: ...I don't know what the captain is thinking.

Thief Nora: But, our new comrades taught me to never give
up, to keep resisting no matter what happens!
Thief Nora: That's why, Captain... I won't let us lose!

Thief Nora: I will save the captain and everyone in the Emma
Thief Gang in my own way!

General Atu: Hahaha, well said! That's right, a battle is a
clash of convictions!

General Atu: And I, as a general, am in a position to
suppress the thief gang. You all are thieves... and enemies
of the empire who protect them.

General Atu: Now then, who will challenge me? The Guild
warriors, the Emma Thief Gang, or the Academy's mages?
Clea: Nora-san, are you okay being alone there?
Thief Nora: Yes, I will definitely stop the captain.

Clea: We will definitely stop General Atu, so please settle
this before then!

Thief Nora: Please watch and see how much the crybaby Nora
has grown!

General Atu: Well then, let me hear your specific plan to
resolve this situation.

General Atu: Is this... some kind of gem? I'm sorry, but I
don't think something like this can solve anything--
Thief Nora: That is the Dragon's Eye.

Thief Nora: This is the genuine Dragon's Eye that the queen
herself asked me to obtain.

Thief Nora: I will give this to the noble person! So please
stop any further attacks!
Thief Nora: H-How is it... ugh

General Atu: Gahaha, very well! As expected, Pido doesn't
possess the Dragon's Eye after all.

General Atu: Leave the negotiations to me. Instruct them to
immediately cease the attack on the Emma Thief Brigade.

Imperial Soldier: It's becoming troublesome, haha. But it's
always like this under the general's command.

General Atu: If we provide a place for Pido to drop his
guard and truly believe that he can crush the thief brigade,
it should work.

General Atu: Politicians are always starting wars, yet they
don't know how to stop them.

General Atu: Nevertheless, it was quite a good fight. I look
forward to the day when we can truly battle seriously.
Clea: Phew, it somehow worked out in the end, didn't it?

Mage Relm: As planned from the beginning... I wanted to
study the Dragon's Eye, though.

Priestess Sophia: There are still many issues regarding what
to do with the captured individuals and the remaining
members of the thief brigade.
Clea: I have an idea for that.
Captain Clevo: ...I will surrender myself to Pido.

Captain Clevo: I don't doubt General Atu, but in exchange
for my own life, I want you to release the comrades who were
captured.
Thief Nora: Captain, can we talk for a moment?

Thief Nora: In a bright place... while basking in the
sunlight.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Thief Nora: Ugh... Captain... I... absolutely... ugh...
ahh...

Captain Clevo: You've become stronger... to the point where
I can hardly recognize you...
Clea: Nora-san! I'm coming to help... Ugh, please wake up!

Captain Clevo: I will leave the general to me. In exchange
for Nora, I will protect the Emma Thief Brigade...
